{
  "title": "ISic000986. Funerary inscription of Auxanon",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag, edition source: </div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>❦ Α 𐆠 Ω ❦ <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>τοίμβος <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σα\n                    βίνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σα\n                    βίνου\">Σα-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>βίνου</span></span> ἐν αὐτῷ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>κῖτε <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αὐξάνων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Αὐξάνων\">Αὐξάνων</span></span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ὁ τούτου υἱὸς <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>βιώσας ἔτη κε´ <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>⸙ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. τοίμβος</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag, edition source: </div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>❦Α𐆠Ω❦<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΤΟΙΜΒΟΣ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σα\n                    βίνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σα\n                    βίνου\">ΣΑ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΒΙΝΟΥ</span></span>ΕΝΑΥΤΩ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΚΙΤΕ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αὐξάνων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Αὐξάνων\">ΑΥΞΑΝΩΝ</span></span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΟΤΟΥΤΟΥΥΙΟΣ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΒΙΩΣΑΣΕΤΗΚΕ<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>⸙</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. τοίμβος</p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>text as per Crispi, Kaibel in IG, Orsi (Kaibel omits the second hedera in line 1)</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Tomb of Sabinos, in this lies Auxanon, son of this man, having lived 25 years</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>One of several inscriptions described by Crispi as coming from Taormina but commonly attributed to Siracusa.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Crispi 1823 264 no.5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002230\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002230</a></li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9466 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">166</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Strazzulla 1897 no. 107 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001390\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001390</a>  </li><li> Rizzo 1904 116 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003144\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003144</a>  </li><li> Wessel 1989 49 no.188 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li><li> Muscolino 2011-2012 234 G22 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215</a>  </li><li> Orsi 2018 Tacc. 2, p.9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002617\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002617</a></li></ul>  <ul><li> Ferrua 1989 no. 481 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</a></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
  "divs": [
    {
